(56, 1, '2023-07-29 07:23:10', '2023-07-29 07:23:10', '<h2>High quality and reliable clock battery for PlayStation 2</h2>\r\nPS2 clock batteries are the highest quality lithium-ion batteries in a small size. High power ensures efficient operation and long service life. Game consoles such as PlayStation 2 require a motherboard battery. Rome Tech batteries are designed to enhance safety. Quality, efficiency and reliability are the basic principles that we use in the manufacturing our products.\r\n<h3>Eco-friendly, powerful and safe</h3>\r\nRome Tech CMOS Battery for PS2 is great for replacing dead battery. High-quality materials and workmanship guarantee a long service life even under extreme conditions. No mercury is used in their production, which makes them environmentally friendly. By purchasing a Rome Tech BIOS battery and installing it in your device, you will be satisfied with the quality of the products.\r\n<h3>Protected and easy to replace</h3>\r\nRome Tech RTC batteries are protected by a cover to reduce the likelihood of damage and accidental discharge. There is an information plate on the battery that confirms the authenticity and informs about the connector for connection. The replacement is simple, no complicated manipulations.\r\n\r\nPS2 CMOS batteries are fully compatible with PlayStation 2 game consoles.', 'Asus ROG CMOS Battery', 'High-quality and reliable CMOS battery for your Lenovo IdeaPad 100-15IBD', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ps2-cmos-battery', '', '', '2023-11-10 15:42:11', '2023-11-10 15:42:11', '', 0, 'http://rtb/?post_type=product&#038;p=56', 0, 'product', '', 1),
